The new-todo input holds an unsubmitted value with leading, trailing, and
internal whitespace. The header value is quoted and verbatim: every space is
significant, nothing is trimmed. Contrast item titles, which are trimmed at the
ends (see `item-title-trimmed.txtar`) — the quotes mark that difference.
Pins: `.new-todo` `.value` read verbatim inside the quotes.

-- dom.html --
<section class="todoapp">
	<header class="header">
		<h1>todos</h1>
		<input class="new-todo" placeholder="What needs to be done?" value="  buy   milk  ">
	</header>
</section>

-- projection.txt --
> "  buy   milk  "
